{"tid":1683870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記者手足，點解唔用鏡反射電筒狗？","createTime":"2019-10-30T23:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:27:11.000Z","uid":335391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d95046c4179033a6c7126d2a40a480ec72227f6b","tid":1683870,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:39:13.000Z","msg":"成日見到你哋做嘢，俾電筒狗照到交唔到貨。<br />\n反正都做唔到嘢,不如下次每人帶一塊化裝鏡反射返強光返去.<br />\n我知啲物理撚話咁樣冇乜power，但係心理撚話啲狗冇咁高IQ去分辨，<br />\n嚇、煩鳩佢都好。<br />\n啲狗亦冇可能拉你哋襲警...<br />\n除非啲狗放屁你撥番轉頭佢都會拉你襲警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n( P牌無力P,   一日一個P )"},{"pid":"3917c5f880c4a6c7594b76176ca59126f8c16bf7","tid":1683870,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:40:50.000Z","msg":"有危險性囉<br />\n<br />\n以今時今日既狗 ,  會特登射爆塊鏡,  碎片爆開仲危險"},{"pid":"67c18751855d8805a668feafd79cba4b557ff3db","tid":1683870,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:47:32.000Z","msg":"光面不鏽鋼呢？"},{"pid":"f6073bc1a2c909c3a0f1ce80a5d4c0cf9b4edd43","tid":1683870,"uid":141270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:14:56.000Z","msg":"啲狗亦冇可能拉你哋襲警...<br />\n<br />\n宜家狗有咩做唔出？<br />\n記者已經夠辛苦<br />\n咪害記者啦<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"61cf0900f9883d00f986d968708fef14baa0719c","tid":1683870,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"d狗見你掛塊鏡出黎<br />\n就知係針對佢地<br />\n睇你唔順眼拉埋番狗屋"},{"pid":"0b9486cea188c1f9ac3b85381f418e7169eef419","tid":1683870,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af2e0fd64636064bf8f90830ac8e172020b024e","tid":1683870,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3917c5f880c4a6c7594b76176ca59126f8c16bf7","tid":1683870,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,